data.description: Cozy Cottage ONE AND A HALF BLOCKS FROM THE RIVER. This home has so much potential , 960 Sq. Ft., two car metal garage, shed and another out building to make your own. THE REFRIGERATOR AND WASHER/DRYER ARE ONE AND A HALF YEARS OLD. THE HVAC WAS REPLACED 2 MONTHS AGO!  The fenced back yard is comfy with a large deck. All this and a short golf cart ride away from the center of town where you can enjoy the beaches, restaurants and shopping. Home is being sold "As is." Colonial Beach is a golf cart community that includes public beaches, public boat ramp, boardwalk, marinas, fabulous restaurants, shops, tiki bars and breweries. Colonial Beach is known as "The Playground on the Potomac."  Walk, hike or ride your bike. An easy ride to explore the wineries of the Northern Neck as well. This is your full time home or weekend getaway, one and 1/2 hours from DC and Richmond and 45 minutes from Fredericksburg. Come on over! Put your toes in the sand!
